  "summary": "In this standard, a non-fungible token stands as atomic existence and encourages layers of abstraction built on top of it. Ideal for representing concepts like rights, a form of abstract ownership. Such right can take the form of NFT options, oracle membership, virtual coupons, etc., and can then be made liquid because of this tokenization.",
